&rdquo;Why do I have to undress?&rdquo;
&rdquo;For physical inspection. I&rsquo;m the type to thoroughly inspect the people coming into my house&rdquo; 

Dreaming of a great gay life, Minjoon came to study in Japan. After being swindled by his ex-lover of six months, Minjoon was ready to end his life but was suddenly surrounded by a group of black Benz cars. Toma, a small boy comes out of a car, running into Minjoon&rsquo;s embrace whilst calling him &ldquo;Mama!&rdquo;. Due to Toma&rsquo;s reluctance, Minjoon is dragged to the yakuza&rsquo;s den where he meets the heartless and fatal Daiki, and thinks it&rsquo;s better to just be killed after seeing Daiki&rsquo;s gaze but&hellip;...
 
This is a thrilling love story of the cold-blooded, and sexy yakuza boss, Daiki Jo, and Minjoon who was chosen to be &ldquo;Mama&rdquo; by Daiki&rsquo;s son, Toma!

[Spanish by Dulce Veneno Yaoi]
